{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2440,"text":"Thank y'all!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":3680,"text":"This is going to be a motivational speech."},{"time":5920,"text":"Because --"},{"time":7680,"text":"imagine my motivation standing\nbetween this strong, healthy crowd ..."},{"time":15600,"text":"and lunch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18560,"text":"So ..."},{"time":21640,"text":"I'm @Falkvinge on Twitter."},{"time":23800,"text":"Feel free to quote me if I say something\nmemorable, stupid, funny, whatever."},{"time":28280,"text":"I love seeing my name on Twitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30040,"text":"So ..."},{"time":31280,"text":"Hi! I'm Rick."},{"time":33520,"text":"I'm a politician."},{"time":35440,"text":"I'm sorry."},{"time":39480,"text":"How many in here have heard\nof the Swedish Pirate Party before?"},{"time":42640,"text":"Let's see a show of hands."},{"time":45240,"text":"OK, that's practically everybody."},{"time":46880,"text":"Probably due to the fact\nthat we are Sweden's neighbor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49520,"text":"I frequently ask how many have heard\nof any other political party"},{"time":53120,"text":"and there's always\njust scattered hands in the audience"},{"time":55760,"text":"compared to this first question\nwhich is one-half to two-thirds."},{"time":59240,"text":"This is actually the first time ever\nthat does not match."},{"time":61960,"text":"It was practically everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64280,"text":"So, for those who haven't heard of us:"},{"time":67920,"text":"well, the Pirate Party, we love the net."},{"time":71320,"text":"We love copying and sharing,\nand we love civil liberties."},{"time":76480,"text":"For that, some people call us pirates."},{"time":79920,"text":"Probably in an attempt to make us\nbow our heads and feel shame."},{"time":82920,"text":"That didn't work very well."},{"time":84280,"text":"We decided to stand tall about it instead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86560,"text":"And so in 2006,\nI founded a new political party."},{"time":90280,"text":"I led it for its first five years."},{"time":92560,"text":"And the European elections,\nthe last European elections,"},{"time":95960,"text":"we became the largest party"},{"time":98400,"text":"and the most coveted\nyouth demographic, sub-30."},{"time":102800,"text":"And what's interesting is we did that"},{"time":104960,"text":"on less than one percent\nof the competition's budget."},{"time":110440,"text":"We had a campaign budget\ntotal of 50,000 euros."},{"time":115080,"text":"They had six million between them --\nand we beat them."},{"time":120440,"text":"That gave us a cost efficiency advantage\nof over two orders of magnitude."},{"time":128320,"text":"And I'm gonna share\nthe secret recipe of how we did that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135440,"text":"We developed swarm methodologies."},{"time":139520,"text":"And they can be applied\nto any business or social cause."},{"time":145640,"text":"Well, almost any --"},{"time":147120,"text":"there's a small asterisk by the end,"},{"time":148880,"text":"and I'll get to that in just a minute."},{"time":151040,"text":"But applying these --"},{"time":152760,"text":"and we've done this dozens of times,\nwe know that this works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156720,"text":"We've put two people\nin the European Parliament,"},{"time":159440,"text":"we have 45 people\nin various German state parliaments,"},{"time":162360,"text":"we're in the Icelandic parliament,\nthe Czech senate,"},{"time":165920,"text":"many, many, many more, local councils --"},{"time":167920,"text":"and, as said, we've spread\nto 70 countries."},{"time":170600,"text":"And that's not bad\nfor a political movement"},{"time":172680,"text":"that hasn't even been around for a decade."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177320,"text":"So today we're going\nto talk a bit about --"},{"time":181360,"text":"how people are motivated\nto be part of change,"},{"time":186320,"text":"to be part of something\nbigger than themselves."},{"time":189760,"text":"And how you can channel this\ninto an organization"},{"time":193880,"text":"that harnesses this great power of wanting\nto make the world a better place."},{"time":201920,"text":"And in the end,\ncome out a little on the better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208120,"text":"When I speak to businesspeople,\nI frequently make them very upset"},{"time":212600,"text":"when I contradict them"},{"time":214480,"text":"and say that no, your employees\nare not your most valuable asset."},{"time":221480,"text":"Your most valuable asset\nis the thousands of people"},{"time":225120,"text":"who want to work for you for free."},{"time":227760,"text":"And you don't let them."},{"time":231000,"text":"They get very upset about that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235480,"text":"A swarm is a congregation\nof tens of thousands of volunteers"},{"time":241840,"text":"that have chosen of their own will\nto converge on a common goal."},{"time":246560,"text":"There's this \"Futurama\" quote:"},{"time":251120,"text":"\"When push comes to shove,\nyou gotta do what you love --"},{"time":256040,"text":"even if it's not a good idea.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":257640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259480,"text":"I mean, seriously,\nwhat kind of idiot thinks"},{"time":261720,"text":"they can change the world\nby starting a political party?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266866,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":268040,"text":"This kind of idiot, apparently."},{"time":269840,"text":"But it works!"},{"time":272840,"text":"What you need to do\nis to put a stake in the ground."},{"time":275320,"text":"You need to announce your goal."},{"time":277480,"text":"Just say, \"I want to accomplish this.\""},{"time":281280,"text":"I'm going to do this."},{"time":284600,"text":"And it doesn't need to be very costly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288040,"text":"My announcement was\njust two lines in a chat channel."},{"time":293680,"text":"\"Hey, look, the Pirate Party\nhas its website up now after New Year's.\""},{"time":297440,"text":"And the address."},{"time":298680,"text":"That was all the advertising I ever did."},{"time":300640,"text":"The next time I had several hundred\nactivists wanting to work with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":305880,"text":"When you provide such a focus point,"},{"time":308360,"text":"a swarm intelligence emerges."},{"time":311320,"text":"When people can rally to a flag."},{"time":314200,"text":"And that's what gives you this two orders\nof magnitude of cost efficiency."},{"time":320440,"text":"It's a huge advantage --"},{"time":322160,"text":"you're running circles\naround all the legacy organizations."},{"time":327160,"text":"And there are four goals\nthat need to be fulfilled in your goal"},{"time":331480,"text":"in order for this to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334440,"text":"These four criteria\nare that your goal must be:"},{"time":338800,"text":"tangible, credible, inclusive and epic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345200,"text":"Let's take a look at them:\nIt needs to be tangible."},{"time":348200,"text":"A lot of people say,"},{"time":349440,"text":"\"Well, you know, we should make\nthe world a better place,\""},{"time":352200,"text":"or, \"Yeah, we should all feel good now.\""},{"time":357360,"text":"Not going to work."},{"time":359440,"text":"You need a binary."},{"time":361680,"text":"Are we there yet, or are we not there yet?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":364360,"text":"It needs to be credible."},{"time":365640,"text":"Somebody seeing the project plan\nthat you're posting needs to see"},{"time":368920,"text":"that, yes, this project plan will take us"},{"time":371040,"text":"from where we are to where we want to be."},{"time":373240,"text":"You need to break it down into subgoals"},{"time":375560,"text":"that each by themselves\nare seen as doable,"},{"time":378480,"text":"and when you add the subgoals together,"},{"time":380920,"text":"we've gone to where we want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383440,"text":"It needs to be --"},{"time":384680,"text":"and this is where it gets exciting\nin terms of working swarmwise --"},{"time":388120,"text":"it needs to be inclusive."},{"time":390000,"text":"Anybody who sees this project plan\nneeds to immediately say,"},{"time":393680,"text":"\"I want to do this --\nand there's my spot!\""},{"time":398360,"text":"And they will be able\nto jump right into the project"},{"time":401880,"text":"and start working on it\nwithout asking anybody's permission."},{"time":407280,"text":"And that is exactly what'll happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410760,"text":"And, last but not least,\nit needs to be epic."},{"time":415440,"text":"It needs to energize people.\nIt needs to electrify people."},{"time":419760,"text":"Shoot for the moon!"},{"time":422840,"text":"On second thought,\ndon't shoot for the moon,"},{"time":424960,"text":"we've already been there --\nshoot for Mars!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":427560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431560,"text":"In contrast,"},{"time":433120,"text":"you will never be able\nto get a volunteer swarm forming"},{"time":438160,"text":"around making the most\ncorrect tax audit ever."},{"time":445200,"text":"Doesn't electrify people. Go to Mars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450040,"text":"A lot of people\nkind of balk at the obstacles."},{"time":452600,"text":"We're going to climb a huge mountain."},{"time":455080,"text":"So how do you motivate people to do that?"},{"time":457320,"text":"Well, it turns out\nthat obstacles are not the problem."},{"time":461080,"text":"Not knowing the obstacles is the problem."},{"time":463960,"text":"If you know how high the mountain is,"},{"time":465800,"text":"you know exactly\nwhat it takes to scale it."},{"time":468360,"text":"We know exactly how far away Mars is\nand what it takes to get there."},{"time":472600,"text":"If you can plan it like a project,"},{"time":475600,"text":"you can plan what resources you need"},{"time":477760,"text":"and you can execute it,\nexactly like a project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480640,"text":"Let's see: we're going to Mars,"},{"time":482200,"text":"we need two dozen\nvolunteer rocket scientists,"},{"time":485360,"text":"one dozen volunteer metallurgists,"},{"time":488320,"text":"some crazy dude who will mix\nrocket fuel in his backyard"},{"time":492880,"text":"and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494920,"text":"When you can list the resources,\nyou know what you need to get there."},{"time":498880,"text":"When you know what you need\nto get there, you can go there."},{"time":504400,"text":"And the next thing is to encourage\nthis development of a swarm intelligence,"},{"time":510680,"text":"which is where\nthe cost efficiency comes in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514120,"text":"There's a TED Talk on motivation\nthat debunks that we work for money,"},{"time":521799,"text":"and it presents science on how\nwe're really motivated by three things,"},{"time":527640,"text":"in terms of larger creative tasks,"},{"time":529320,"text":"when we work for something\nbigger than ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532320,"text":"We work for autonomy, mastery and purpose."},{"time":538120,"text":"We've covered purpose already."},{"time":540160,"text":"As in, working for something bigger,\ntangible, credible, inclusive and epic."},{"time":546240,"text":"So, where that motivation talk ends,"},{"time":550480,"text":"what it doesn't answer is,"},{"time":553920,"text":"how do you build an organization\nthat harnesses this motivational power."},{"time":559840,"text":"And this is where\nworking swarmwise comes in,"},{"time":562200,"text":"this is where swarm intelligence comes in."},{"time":564680,"text":"Turns out that there are three factors\nthat you optimize for --"},{"time":568240,"text":"and each of these are in complete opposite\nto what you learn at a business school."},{"time":574600,"text":"But it works."},{"time":576200,"text":"We know it works."},{"time":577840,"text":"We have people in many, many\nparliaments to prove it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582640,"text":"Those three factors are:\nspeed, trust and scalability."},{"time":589160,"text":"We optimize for speed\nby cutting bottlenecks out of the loop,"},{"time":593680,"text":"cutting them out of the decision loop."},{"time":595560,"text":"That means cutting yourself\nout of the decision loop,"},{"time":599160,"text":"which can be hard."},{"time":600680,"text":"But you've got to communicate your vision\nso passionately, so strongly,"},{"time":606000,"text":"that everybody knows what the goal is"},{"time":609400,"text":"and can find something, some step"},{"time":612200,"text":"that takes the movement\njust a little closer to that goal."},{"time":616560,"text":"And when tens of thousands of people\ndo that on a weekly basis,"},{"time":621440,"text":"you become an unstoppable force."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624560,"text":"We had a three-person rule\nin our organization,"},{"time":627800,"text":"saying that if three self-identified\nvolunteers in the movement"},{"time":631200,"text":"were in agreement that something\nwas good for the movement,"},{"time":634040,"text":"they had the green light\nfrom the highest office"},{"time":636320,"text":"to go ahead and act\nin the name of the organization,"},{"time":638800,"text":"including spending resources."},{"time":641360,"text":"When you talk about\nthis kind of empowerment"},{"time":643480,"text":"to traditional businesspeople,"},{"time":645360,"text":"they think you belong in a zoo."},{"time":648440,"text":"But you know what?"},{"time":650200,"text":"I led this organization for five years,"},{"time":653400,"text":"there were 50,000 registered members"},{"time":657640,"text":"and many, many more anonymous activists."},{"time":660640,"text":"It was not abused once."},{"time":664240,"text":"Everybody had the key\nto the treasure chest."},{"time":666480,"text":"It was not abused one single time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":669600,"text":"Turns out when you give people\nthe keys to the castle,"},{"time":672520,"text":"and look them in the eye\nand say, \"I trust you,\""},{"time":677480,"text":"they step up to the plate."},{"time":680280,"text":"And that's a beautiful thing\nto see happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684400,"text":"Obviously, not everything\nwent according to plan,"},{"time":686760,"text":"but that's a different thing."},{"time":688200,"text":"We made mistakes.\nWe should expect mistakes."},{"time":690640,"text":"If you're pioneering something,\nthat means you must, by definition,"},{"time":694320,"text":"venture into the unknown."},{"time":696200,"text":"When you're trying the unknown,\nsome things won't go as planned."},{"time":699320,"text":"That's part of the definition\nof venturing into the unknown."},{"time":702240,"text":"To find the great,\nyou must allow mistakes to happen."},{"time":706360,"text":"So you must communicate\nthat we expect some things to go wrong"},{"time":710240,"text":"to create a risk-positive environment."},{"time":715040,"text":"Therefore we optimize for iteration speed."},{"time":719760,"text":"Meaning that we try, we fail,\nwe try again, we fail faster,"},{"time":724240,"text":"we fail better, we try again,\nwe fail better again."},{"time":727640,"text":"Maybe after we've tried 15 times,\nwe've mastered some specific subject,"},{"time":732000,"text":"so you want to minimize the time\nit takes to try those 15 times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736320,"text":"We optimize on trust.\nWe encourage diversity."},{"time":739440,"text":"You need to communicate\nyour vision so strongly"},{"time":741720,"text":"so that everybody can translate it\ninto their own context"},{"time":746640,"text":"because language is an incredibly strong"},{"time":750560,"text":"inclusionary and exclusionary\nsocial marker."},{"time":756800,"text":"This one-brand-fits-all message --"},{"time":760080,"text":"forget it!"},{"time":761320,"text":"That's what they teach you\nat business school -- it doesn't work."},{"time":764440,"text":"Or at least, it doesn't give you\nthe cost-efficiency advantage"},{"time":768640,"text":"of working swarmwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772920,"text":"This leads to a lot of different\napproaches tried in parallel"},{"time":775840,"text":"in different social groups"},{"time":777480,"text":"who try out different methods\nof working toward the goal."},{"time":782080,"text":"Some of them will work"},{"time":783960,"text":"but in order to find the great ones,\nyou need this diversity."},{"time":788040,"text":"And you need to communicate\nthat we need that diversity."},{"time":791520,"text":"If somebody on this side\ndoes not understand"},{"time":794200,"text":"what those guys are doing,"},{"time":796240,"text":"that's OK because we all trust each other\nto work for the better of the movement."},{"time":800480,"text":"And it's OK that I don't understand\ntheir social context."},{"time":803960,"text":"I'm not expected to --\nI understand my social context."},{"time":806560,"text":"I contribute with something I know."},{"time":809720,"text":"Make people aware of this diversity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811480,"text":"Finally, scalability.\nGet feet on the ground."},{"time":814880,"text":"Again, in business school,\nthey teach you to use a lean organization."},{"time":818360,"text":"Forget that."},{"time":820320,"text":"Just scale up the organization\nfrom the get-go."},{"time":822560,"text":"Start with 10,000 empty boxes\nand an org chart"},{"time":825480,"text":"covering down to every minor city."},{"time":828680,"text":"When you have lots and lots\nof small responsibilities"},{"time":831880,"text":"in such a scaffolding\nthat supports the swarm,"},{"time":835440,"text":"supports the activists,"},{"time":837000,"text":"you'll find that these boxes\nin the org charts"},{"time":841040,"text":"are getting filled in quite rapidly,"},{"time":844280,"text":"and they start to get filled in\nbeyond your horizon"},{"time":846840,"text":"with people you've never heard of."},{"time":849480,"text":"And so, this swarm keeps growing\nto tens of thousands of people,"},{"time":856000,"text":"each taking on something small\nwith very, very decentralized mandate"},{"time":861400,"text":"to act on the organization."},{"time":863480,"text":"And this is when\na swarm intelligence emerges."},{"time":866760,"text":"This is when you have this beehive logic\nwhere everybody knows what's to be done."},{"time":872200,"text":"Everybody is taking\ntheir own small steps towards it."},{"time":875800,"text":"So the swarm starts to act\nas a coherent organism."},{"time":881360,"text":"And it's amazing to watch."},{"time":884000,"text":"This is when you're awarded\nby the cost-efficiency advantage"},{"time":888200,"text":"over your competitors"},{"time":891400,"text":"by two orders of magnitude."},{"time":895000,"text":"Two orders of magnitude."},{"time":897360,"text":"This is not just a silver bullet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900680,"text":"So we've been talking a lot\nabout the big picture today."},{"time":904720,"text":"You can use these swarm methods\nfor a lot of stuff."},{"time":907160,"text":"Do you want to change the world?"},{"time":909040,"text":"Do you want to bring clean water\nto a billion people?"},{"time":911560,"text":"Teach three billion people to read?"},{"time":913280,"text":"Maybe you're into social change;"},{"time":914880,"text":"you want to introduce\nunconditional basic income."},{"time":917520,"text":"Or maybe you want\nto take humanity to Mars."},{"time":920280,"text":"You can do this using these methods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":923360,"text":"You can do this."},{"time":924800,"text":"It's about leadership."},{"time":926040,"text":"It's about deciding what you want to do\nand telling it to the world."},{"time":931560,"text":"Because no matter whether you think\nyou can or cannot change the world,"},{"time":938680,"text":"no matter whether you think\nyou can or cannot change the world,"},{"time":943080,"text":"you are probably right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":948160,"text":"So one question I want everybody here\nto ask themselves today"},{"time":952480,"text":"is the observation that change doesn't\njust happen, somebody makes it happen --"},{"time":959560,"text":"do you want to be that person?"},{"time":962800,"text":"Do you want to be that person?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":966480,"text":"And then one last thing:"},{"time":972440,"text":"There's one component more\nthat's required to work swarmwise"},{"time":976040,"text":"that I haven't mentioned yet."},{"time":978400,"text":"And that is fun."},{"time":981600,"text":"This goes beyond just enjoying your job,"},{"time":984600,"text":"this goes beyond having\na pinball machine in the office."},{"time":989520,"text":"Because this is actually required\nto succeed in a swarmwise scenario."},{"time":995680,"text":"This is required to succeed"},{"time":997400,"text":"to get that cost-efficiency advantage\nof two orders of magnitude."},{"time":1002640,"text":"For the reason that you need\nto attract volunteers."},{"time":1006720,"text":"And people, in this aspect,\nare rather predictable."},{"time":1011600,"text":"People will go to other people\nwho are having fun."},{"time":1017240,"text":"In contrast, they will walk an extra mile\nto avoid people who are not having fun."},{"time":1026400,"text":"So, having fun is more than just\nhaving a pinball machine in the office."},{"time":1032319,"text":"It's an absolute\nand unavoidable requirement"},{"time":1037319,"text":"for organizational and operational success\nwhen you're working swarmwise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1042920,"text":"So, in summary --"},{"time":1047040,"text":"a recipe for a swarm organization"},{"time":1050440,"text":"using these motivational methods\nto a huge competitive advantage."},{"time":1057560,"text":"Your goal: it needs to be tangible,\ncredible, inclusive and epic."},{"time":1065880,"text":"Your organization needs to be optimized\nfor speed, trust and scalability."},{"time":1073000,"text":"You need to enjoy yourselves."},{"time":1075440,"text":"And that will reward you"},{"time":1077080,"text":"with two orders of magnitude\nof cost-efficiency advantage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1081360,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1082600,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}